Command,Description
ls,List file names only
ll,List files with details (alias for ls -l)
ll -a,Show hidden files
ll -t,Sort by time (newest first)
ll -ltr,"Long listing, sorted by time, in reverse (newest at bottom)"
cat file,Read file content
tac file,Read file content in reverse (last line first)
rev file,Reverse the characters in each line
head -n 10,Show first 10 lines
tail -n 10,Show last 10 lines
more file,View file with page percentages
wc -l file,Count lines in a file
